## What is GENY?

ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google SGE now answer product questions directly вҖ” without sending users to your page. If your product page isn't structured for AI, **you are invisible**.

**GENY** crawls any product page, scores it across 5 AI readiness dimensions, and runs a 4-agent AI pipeline that tells you exactly what HTML, schema, and content changes to make вҖ” with copy-paste fixes.

```
Your product URL  вҶ’  GENY crawls it  вҶ’  Scores AI visibility  вҶ’  4 agents analyze it  вҶ’  Executive report with exact fixes
```

---

## The Problem GENY Solves

| What users ask AI | What happens without GEO | What happens with GENY |
|---|---|---|
| "Best running shoes under вӮ№5000?" | AI ignores your page, cites competitor | Your page gets cited |
| "Does this bookcase fit in 80cm space?" | AI can't extract your specs | AI reads your specs table directly |
| "Is this product warrantied?" | No warranty schema вҶ’ not cited | JSON-LD warranty field вҶ’ cited |
| "Where can I buy X brand tank top?" | Missing entity signals вҶ’ invisible | GTIN + brand schema вҶ’ knowledge graph |

