## 4-Agent AI Pipeline

GENY uses a **LangGraph StateGraph** where each agent receives the full structured context and builds on the previous agent's output.

```
llm_context dict
      в”Ӯ
      в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  Agent 1        в”Ӯ  вҶҗ System: "Senior AI SEO technical auditor"
в”Ӯ  Technical      в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Exact HTML/JSON-LD snippets for every failing signal
в”Ӯ  Auditor        в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Copy-paste fixes for canonical, hreflang, schema
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
         в”Ӯ
         в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  Agent 2        в”Ӯ  вҶҗ System: "World-class GEO content strategist"  
в”Ӯ  Content        в”Ӯ  вҶ’ 6 real FAQ Q&As with JSON-LD schema block
в”Ӯ  Strategist     в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Missing content sections with actual text to add
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
         в”Ӯ
         в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  Agent 3        в”Ӯ  вҶҗ System: "Senior AI visibility consultant"
в”Ӯ  Prioritizer    в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Priority table: Quick Wins vs Structural
в”Ӯ                 в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Score projection: current вҶ’ after wins вҶ’ after all
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
         в”Ӯ
         в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  Agent 4        в”Ӯ  вҶҗ System: "Strategic AI optimization advisor (CMO audience)"
в”Ӯ  Report         в”Ӯ  вҶ’ Executive summary referencing exact scores
в”Ӯ  Builder        в”Ӯ  вҶ’ What happens if you fix nothing
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
         в”Ӯ
         в–ј
  { technical_analysis, content_analysis,
    prioritized_plan, executive_summary }
```

---

## Scoring System

GENY scores pages out of **100 points** across 5 dimensions:

| Dimension | Max | What it measures |
|-----------|-----|-----------------|
| **Schema Markup** | 20 | JSON-LD Product schema, price, brand, availability, ratings |
| **Entity Clarity** | 15 | Product name quality, brand, SKU, category, GTIN |
| **Content Depth** | 25 | Word count, headings, features, specifications, FAQ |
| **Trust Signals** | 20 | Return policy, warranty, shipping, HTTPS, reviews, contact |
| **Extractability** | 20 | Canonical URL, meta tags, specs table, hreflang, heading hierarchy |

**Readiness Bands:**
```
85вҖ“100  Excellent   в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳ  AI engines will cite this page
70вҖ“84   Good        в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–‘в–‘  Minor fixes needed
50вҖ“69   Fair        в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘  Significant gaps вҖ” losing citations
30вҖ“49   Poor        в–Ҳв–Ҳв–Ҳв–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘  Major structural issues
0вҖ“29    Critical    в–Ҳв–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘в–‘  Essentially invisible to AI
```

