## Project Structure

```
geny/
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ project/                    # Backend
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ crawler.py              # ProductCrawler вҖ” scrapes pages
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ scoring.py              # AIScoringEngine вҖ” 100pt scoring
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ llm_context.py          # LLMContextBuilder вҖ” structured context
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ geo.py                  # LangGraph 4-agent pipeline
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.py                 # FastAPI app вҖ” 4 endpoints
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ data/                   # Saved crawl + context JSON files
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ Procfile                # For Railway deployment
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ .env                    # OPENAI_API_KEY (never commit)
в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җ frontend/                   # React frontend
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ src/
    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ GeoOptimizer.jsx    # Entire frontend вҖ” single component
    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ index.js            # React entry point
    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ App.js              # Mounts GeoOptimizer
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ public/
    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ index.html
    в””в”Җв”Җ package.json
```

