## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 18, inline CSS, SVG animations |
| Backend | FastAPI, Python 3.10+ |
| AI Pipeline | LangGraph, OpenAI GPT-4o-mini |
| Web Scraping | requests, BeautifulSoup4, lxml |
| Schema Parsing | extruct, json-ld |
| Deployment | Vercel (frontend) + Railway (backend) |
| Fonts | Syne В· Space Mono В· DM Sans (Google Fonts) |

